  <text>
    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Like the waves making way towards the show</l>
            <l>So do our time come to an end,</l>
            <l>Each moment replacing those made before,</l>
            <l>workig hard towards feeling happiness.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l><name type="person">Jesus</name> birth, once in the spotlight,</l>
            <l>Slowly grows older while being praised,</l>
            <l>Slight insight into his victorious fight,</l>
            <l>And the giving time does now reveal <choice><orig>it's</orig><reg>its</reg></choice> gifts.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Time changes the view set on youth</l>
            <l>And hides the <choice><orig>paralles</orig><reg>parallels</reg></choice> of the most beauty,</l>
            <l>Takes advantage of nature rarities,</l>
            <l>And nothing stands but his scythe to cut grass.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>In times of hope my love should stay,</l>
            <l>Praising your worth, despite his cruel hand.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
